snippet: At least 16 insurgents from the Nusra Front were killed in an attack on Hezbollah bases along a mountain range close to the Syrian border.
abstract: At least 16 insurgents from the Nusra Front, Al Qaeda's wing in Syria, are killed in an attack on Hezbollah bases in eastern Lebanon.
lead_paragraph: At least 16 insurgents from the Nusra Front were killed in an attack on Hezbollah bases along a mountain range close to the Syrian border.

headline.main: Al Qaeda Affiliate Battles Hezbollah in Lebanon
